==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''asthma'''

# {{pathology}} A chronic respiratory disease, in which the [[airway]]s unexpectedly and suddenly narrow, often in response to an [[allergen]], cold air, exercise, or emotional stress. Symptoms include wheezing, shortness of breath, chest tightness, and coughing.

